42
00:03:41,021 --> 00:03:41,855
- Daddy?

43
00:03:47,861 --> 00:03:50,531
- [Narrator] I saw
mi papi die that day.

44
00:03:50,531 --> 00:03:52,333
And I swore I would
have my revenge.

45
00:03:54,735 --> 00:03:57,237
(upbeat music)

46
