Daddy package.

79
00:06:41,435 --> 00:06:44,204
You were so much
fun to grow up with.

80
00:06:44,237 --> 00:06:45,405
- Yes!

81
00:06:45,405 --> 00:06:47,675
- [Cheni] And once
those bad men took me,

82
