get out of here, John.

198
00:13:41,154 --> 00:13:44,157
Find a nice, quiet place and
start a new life for yourself.

199
00:13:45,125 --> 00:13:46,759
- I can't do that, General.

200
00:13:46,759 --> 00:13:49,930
