I've go to save her!

201
00:13:49,930 --> 00:13:51,598
- Are you feeling okay, John?

202
00:13:51,631 --> 00:13:53,934
That was a long time ago.

203
00:13:53,934 --> 00:13:55,335
- I know that she's grown up.

204
00:13:55,335 --> 00:13:56,870
