was going to kill you last?

221
00:14:41,881 --> 00:14:43,750
- That's right,
Mantrixx, you did!

222
00:14:44,684 --> 00:14:46,486
- I lied.

223
00:14:46,486 --> 00:14:49,089
(screams)

224
00:14:49,089 --> 00:14:51,391
