to start digging.

227
00:14:57,064 --> 00:14:58,531
- I'll check it out, General.

228
00:14:59,832 --> 00:15:01,268
- And in case things get rough.

229
00:15:03,236 --> 00:15:04,337
Welcome back, John.

230
00:15:05,505 --> 00:15:07,740
You and I are the
last of a dying breed,

231
00:15:07,740 --> 00:15:10,577
